            </h4>
            <h6 class="text-media__sub-title regular">
                Making Better People Decisions
            </h6>
            <div class="text-media__description">
                <p>
                    People are an organization&#x27;s most valuable asset, largest cost, and also a major source of risk― therefore, getting your people strategy right can often be the difference between success or failure. Our Human Capital products and advisors help clients navigate today&#x27;s most pressing people challenges to create a healthier, more engaged, and ultimately more productive workforce.
                </p>
